(62,	'SIDBI/G/2019/06/25/000062',	'Pravin Gupta',	'CredenTek Software and Consultancy Pvt Ltd',	'303 Pride Purple Accord',	'Pune',	'Maharashtra',	'INDIA',	'411045',	'9890633500',	'9890633500',	'pravin.gupta@credentek.com',	'Wrong AGF fees charged for my CGTMSE Limit through IDFC First Bank',	'Respected Sir\r\n\r\nMy complaint is about wrong fees charged in CGTMSE scheme offered by SIDBI to MSME organizations\r\n\r\n1 In Jun 2018 my organization availed CGTMSE limit of 1 Crore through IDFC First Bank Mumbai\r\n2 On 06 Mar 2019 CGTMSE AGF fees of Rs 106027 was charged even when there was no utilization of limit\r\n3 As per the RBI circular CGS 1 dated 21 Aug 18 second year AGF fees will be charged only on utilized limit \r\nHowever in my case AGF fees was charged on full limit amount\r\n4 When I approached IDFC First Bank I received unsatisfactory explanation\r\n\r\nAs per bank explanation\r\na If there is an utilization of limit AGF fees will be calculated on utilized amount\r\nb If no utilization of limit AGF fees will be charged on FULL limit amount \r\nThis is completely against RBI circular for fees calculation\r\n\r\nSir  how can SIDBI charge and penalize a MSME by applying AGF fees on full limit amount when limit utilization is zero\r\n',	'2019-06-25 17:57:18',	'2019-06-25 12:27:19'),
